details.body:
The following information is provided to answer common queries you may have when comparing search results obtained prior to the service moving to HM Land Registry’s Local Land Charges (LLC) service. Please choose the relevant local authority area for your search results explanation.

You can find out more about the local land charges live service.

  1. LLC search service (PDF, 615 KB, 5 pages)
  2. Search result example (PDF, 7.03 MB, 2 pages)
